The paper deals with domain adaptation for videos, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves learning temporal dynamics, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of adversarial training, which is a popular technique in deep learning (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
